Name: Humans
Description: Specifies custom values to be added to "/www/public/humans.txt" in addition to the auto-generate values. The conf2 extension indicates it is processed seperate from other configuration files in this folder by the system.
Destination: /humans.txt
Content:
"
/* TEAM */
$role: $name
Site: $url
Location: $town, $country

/* THANKS */
$role: $name
Site: $url
Location: $town, $country
"